---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Directory Website Agency | Stackbase System" description="Stackbase System helps founders and teams launch US-focused directory websites that are fast, SEO-ready, and built to convert.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="text-sm text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-wider">DIRECTORY WEBSITE AGENCY</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-5 font-['Space_Grotesk']">We build directory websites that rank, load fast, and sell your niche authority</h1>
      <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg max-w-3xl">Stackbase System is focused on one thing: production-ready directory websites for US-focused markets. You get clear scope, conversion-focused UX, technical SEO from day one, and a build you can actually maintain after launch.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5"><p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Typical Core Delivery</p><p class="text-white text-2xl font-['JetBrains_Mono'] mt-1">~14 days</p></div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5"><p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Communication Style</p><p class="text-white mt-1">Async-first, fast response loops</p></div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5"><p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Build Priority</p><p class="text-white mt-1">SEO architecture + buyer clarity</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">What gets delivered</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]">
          <li>• Homepage + directory template system designed for conversion</li>
          <li>• Listing pages that support search intent, not just visual polish</li>
          <li>• Search/filter UX that helps users discover listings quickly</li>
          <li>• Technical SEO baseline: sitemap, canonical, schema, metadata</li>
          <li>• Structured data import support (BYOD-friendly)</li>
          <li>• Launch QA + handoff notes for confident operation post-launch</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">Why founders hire Stackbase</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]">
          <li>• They need a real operator, not generic agency fluff</li>
          <li>• They want a clean system instead of plugin-heavy chaos</li>
          <li>• They care about search visibility and trust signals early</li>
          <li>• They prefer a transparent build scope and async workflow</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">Who this is best for</h2>
        <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] mb-5">This service is ideal for founders launching niche directories, teams replacing old WordPress stacks, and operators who want to scale into programmatic SEO without sacrificing page quality.</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-[#c7c7d2]">
          <p>• You need speed + credibility to start selling quickly</p>
          <p>• You have data (or plan to enrich it) and need clean structure</p>
          <p>• You want a site that feels premium from day one</p>
          <p>• You want clear project boundaries with optional add-ons</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f0ff] to-[#00c8ff] rounded-xl">See pricing and scope</a>
      <a href="/portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">Review portfolio proof</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">Send project brief</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
